    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0002",
      "text": " 151",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0003",
      "text": "The Common Service Parameters Payload for PLOGI and PLOGI LS_ACC is shown in table 152.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        527.08,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0004",
      "text": "The Common Service Parameters Payload for FLOGI LS_ACC is shown in table 153.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.97,
        473.68,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0005",
      "text": "6.6.2.3  Buffer-to-buffer Credit",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.97,
        237.51,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0006",
      "text": "The buffer-to-buffer Credit field (word 0, bits 15-0) defines the number of buffers available for holding",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.97,
        539.89,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0007",
      "text": "Class 1 and Class 6 connect-request, Class 2, or Class 3 frames received.  An FC_Port tracks Buff-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.97,
        539.96,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0008",
      "text": "er-to-buffer Credit as a single entity for all frames subject to buffer-to-buffer flow control (see FC-FS-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.94,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0009",
      "text": "2).  Values in the Buffer-to-buffer Credit field are 1 to 32767. The value 0 is reserved.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        470.9,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0010",
      "text": "For N_Port Login, this field shall only be meaningful for an Nx_Port in a point-to-point topology and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        539.88,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0011",
      "text": "between two NL_Ports on the same loop.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        278.74,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0012",
      "text": "6.6.2.4  Common Features",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        219.83,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0013",
      "text": "6.6.2.4.1  Continuously increasing relative offset",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        324.94,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0014",
      "text": "0 = not supported",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        174.01,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0015",
      "text": "1 = supported",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        157.4,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0016",
      "text": "If the continuously increasing relative offset bit (word 1, bit 31) is set to one, the Nx_Port supplying",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.99,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0017",
      "text": "this parameter shall be capable of supporting continuously increasing relative offset, if present",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.97,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0018",
      "text": "(F_CTL bit 3), within a Sequence on a frame by frame SEQ_CNT basis.  This bit shall only be appli-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        540.03,
        646.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0019",
      "text": "cable to those Information Categories in which an Nx_Port supports relative offset (i.e., word 2, bits",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        540.03,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0020",
      "text": "15-0).  See FC-FS-2 for the use of continuously increasing relative offset.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        419.25,
        670.14
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0021",
      "text": "This bit shall be applicable to a Sequence Initiator in addition to a Sequence Recipient for all Classes",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        540.01,
        694.14
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p170_s0022",
      "text": "of Service supported by the Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        695.02,
        259.34,
        706.14
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
